  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Hotels</strong></p>
<p>Bergen (3/4 nights) <a href="/%7blocalLink:umb:/document/0d46aba9adc646f2afb1eeefe50bbc3f%7d">Augustin</a> ★★★+ <span>A friendly family-run hotel, beautifully decorated with a welcoming atmosphere and many special touches. Centrally situated which makes the harbour, fish market and Bryggen Wharf approximately a 3-4 minute walk (350m). This hotel is a great choice to explore this fascinating city, conveniently located to shops and a good selection of international restaurants.</span></p>
<p>Balestrand (4/3 nights) <a href="/%7blocalLink:umb:/document/e6e72ed8f54b4b799df9821bf732b69d%7d">Midtnes</a> ★★+ A small, homely hotel with a relaxed atmosphere, attentive personal service from your host, Jon, and panoramic views.  The Midtnes is located in a peaceful spot just next door to St. Olaf's Church and enjoys its own fjord side garden as well as offers panoramic fjord views from its sun terrace. Guests here are sure of a warm welcome. </p>
<p><strong>OR</strong></p>
<p><strong>Superior Hotels</strong></p>
<p>Bergen (3/4 nights) <a href="/%7blocalLink:umb:/document/9d0bff3ead764e2784c07e601d199b65%7d">First Hotel Marin</a> ★★★+ <span>In an enviable, harbour front location, convenient for Bergen’s main attractions, this elegant hotel offers good facilities and spacious, comfortable rooms.  Located in an old wharf building, Bergen's main sights of the harbour, fish market and Fløiban funicular are only a few steps away.</span></p>
<p>Balestrand (4/3 nights) <a href="/%7blocalLink:umb:/document/d26dcba440054402b9ccfe7166c1ad56%7d">Kviknes</a> ★★★★ <span>This wonderfully atmospheric historic dates back to 1752. Today with its modern amenities, main wing and attentive personal service it remains one of Fjord Norway’s best loved, family-run properties. The attractive original Swiss style wing radiates personality and soul, with an absolutely magnificent scenic fjord-side location and panoramic views across the Sognefjord.</span></p>]]></roomsDescription>
